Package: buildGPT
Title: Fine-tuning and model builder for OpenAI
Version: 0.0.1
Description: Provides functions to create, monitor, and delete fine-tuned models using the OpenAI API. 
    This package includes robust error handling and utility functions to facilitate interactions with the API.
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
